REM Jan 13 MSG Steve's birthday
REM Feb 18 ++7 MSG Mom & Dad's anniversary
REM Apr 1 ++1 MSG April Fool's Day
REM Sun AT 9:00 MSG Church
REM 15 MSG Invoice customers

# repeats on a schedule
